  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/9fcfe1089635116516682c6d001bfcfe.poster.avif?t=1726271519\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/9fcfe1089635116516682c6d001bfcfe.webm?t=1726271519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/9fcfe1089635116516682c6d001bfcfe.mp4?t=1726271519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Once your character is chosen, step into the vibrant hub. Launch into battles, enhance stats, acquire potent spell upgrades, and unlock new mystical abilities. Immerse yourself in the tournament's narrative by engaging in conversations with other players and townfolk.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/25b8ce017f684819ec25c970575b6f52.poster.avif?t=1726271519\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/25b8ce017f684819ec25c970575b6f52.webm?t=1726271519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/25b8ce017f684819ec25c970575b6f52.mp4?t=1726271519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Day 1 - Fights!<br>Day 2 - Shops open (upgrades & spells), guilds open at night<br>Day 3 - Choose augment at night<br>Day 4-6 - Fights!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/595a795b758ba3daed28d804120cad8e.webp?t=1726271519\" width=602 height=45 /></span><br>On the second night of the tournament, enter the Guild Portal and select your destiny. Join the ranks of the <strong>Shaman</strong>, <strong>Alchemist</strong>, <strong>Dragon Tamer</strong>, or <strong>Witch</strong> guilds. Each guild presents a distinct quest, offering a meaningful choice that shapes your character's path—commit to one guild and embrace the rewards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/25c2f78174c46e359f20e90b57c63360.webp?t=1726271519\" width=602 height=45 /></span><br>Unleash your creativity in Versus mode, where all characters (some require unlocking) and spells are at your disposal. With a thousand possible mix-and-match loadouts, dive into endless experimentation and craft your unique playstyle in the magical arena.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/9fcfe1089635116516682c6d001bfcfe.poster.avif?t=1726271519\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/9fcfe1089635116516682c6d001bfcfe.webm?t=1726271519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/9fcfe1089635116516682c6d001bfcfe.mp4?t=1726271519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Once your character is chosen, step into the vibrant hub. Launch into battles, enhance stats, acquire potent spell upgrades, and unlock new mystical abilities. Immerse yourself in the tournament's narrative by engaging in conversations with other players and townfolk.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/25b8ce017f684819ec25c970575b6f52.poster.avif?t=1726271519\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/25b8ce017f684819ec25c970575b6f52.webm?t=1726271519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/25b8ce017f684819ec25c970575b6f52.mp4?t=1726271519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Day 1 - Fights!<br>Day 2 - Shops open (upgrades & spells), guilds open at night<br>Day 3 - Choose augment at night<br>Day 4-6 - Fights!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/595a795b758ba3daed28d804120cad8e.webp?t=1726271519\" width=602 height=45 /></span><br>On the second night of the tournament, enter the Guild Portal and select your destiny. Join the ranks of the <strong>Shaman</strong>, <strong>Alchemist</strong>, <strong>Dragon Tamer</strong>, or <strong>Witch</strong> guilds. Each guild presents a distinct quest, offering a meaningful choice that shapes your character's path—commit to one guild and embrace the rewards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196240/extras/25c2f78174c46e359f20e90b57c63360.webp?t=1726271519\" width=602 height=45 /></span><br>Unleash your creativity in Versus mode, where all characters (some require unlocking) and spells are at your disposal. With a thousand possible mix-and-match loadouts, dive into endless experimentation and craft your unique playstyle in the magical arena.",
